25060 DATA"you can move snakey (o) by those "
25070 DATA"letters which i will show you in a moment. "
25080 DATA"the letter in the middle "
25090 DATA"stands for the momentary "
25100 DATA"position of snakey. "
25110 DATA"pressing one of the other "
25120 DATA"shown keys will "
25130 DATA"make him wander into "
25140 DATA"that direction. "
25150 DATA"if snakey happens to "
25160 DATA"walk upon a '%', he "
25170 DATA"eats it and dies "
25180 DATA"because it is poison. "
25190 DATA"and when he walks upon "
25200 DATA"a '$' he will become "
25210 DATA"1 cm longer. "
25220 DATA"but do also be cautious "
25230 DATA"not to run against the "
25240 DATA"walls!! "
25250 DATA"thus, your task is to breed "
25260 DATA"up snakey and to make him "
25270 DATA"as long as possible. "
25280 DATA"each cm will be counted "
25290 DATA"as a point for you. "
